text: Very nice, helpful and friendly staff. Price is cheap and reasonable. I always buy Med and stuffs here for HK. Highly recommended.

Traditional Chinese Medicine hall riding into the 21st century , updated to serve people of these times. Folksy friendly staff. Raw medicinal herbs are not pricey ( the ones that is prescribed by your Chinese Sin Seh ). Not sure about the rest though ( because I didn't buy them and compare them ) . Can pay with CDC vouchers too !
Very good service. Very comprehensive chinese medicine.
Good and friendly service. Price is affordable ✌️
